=head2 setbadif

=for sig

  Signature: (a(); int mask(); [o]b())

=for ref

Set elements bad based on the supplied mask, otherwise
copy across the data.

=for example

 pdl> $a = sequence(5,5)
 pdl> $a = $a->setbadif( $a % 2 )
 pdl> p "a badflag: ", $a->badflag, "\n"
 a badflag: 1
 pdl> p "a is\n$a"
 [
  [  0 BAD   2 BAD   4]
